page.title: 19Tree types in our D'block.
page.content: The different types of trees in our {'D'block}are,oak,sycamore,beech,silver birch,lilac,maple,horse chestnut,ash, lime,sweet chestnut,holly,elm,birch, hazel,apple,scots pine and weeping willow.There are 7 woods in our 'D' block.In the first square there are 3} woods.Tese are mainly oak and maple but one has got some conifers in.In square 2 there are no woods but there is a orchard.In squares 3 and 4 there are no woods because it is mainly housing.In square 5 there is 1 wood and that is decidcious.The next woods are in squares 7 and 8.There are 2 woods in square 7 and 1 wood in square 8.In the next 4 squares there are no woods because both squares are mainly housing estates.
